&lt;p&gt;As a Consultant on the Staff Augmentation team, you will partner with healthcare customers as an extension of their internal teams to administer and optimize their Strata Decision Support solutions. In this role, you will manage day-to-day system administration, support ongoing maintenance and enhancements, and drive adoption initiatives to ensure cost accounting solutions remain effective, scalable, and aligned to evolving operational and strategic needs. Through close collaboration with customer stakeholders, you will help organizations maximize the value of their Strata investment. In each of the responsibilities below, you will have the support and guidance from a senior team member to ensure team member development and customer success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Perform the solution administrator functions including data reconciliation, cost model configuration/auditing and reporting within the Decision Support solution with high quality and high customer satisfaction following the service protocols that have been established.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Partner with the customer and sr. team members to identify, communicate and implement DS enhancement items to increase cost accuracy and/or cost model efficiency projects.&lt;/li&gt;
