&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You’ll Make an Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Consultant on our Planning &amp;amp; Performance Management (PPM) Advisory Services team, you’ll partner with healthcare organizations to help them adopt and optimize StrataJazz® solutions for financial planning, forecasting, budgeting, and performance management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll guide customers in translating data into actionable insights, shaping planning processes, and establishing the workflows and structures needed to support effective decision-making. This role blends advisory, facilitation, and structured execution to help organizations improve financial performance and operational alignment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with customers to understand goals, priorities, and current state processes to help define the scope and approach for advisory engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate working sessions and discussions to align on planning processes, performance management practices, and key decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate financial and operational data into clear insights and actionable recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help design and refine planning processes, including budgeting, forecasting, and performance review processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver roadmap materials, presentations, and documentation for stakeholders across finance and operational leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on how to effectively leverage StrataJazz® PPM capabilities, including data structure, workflow design, and integration considerations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support elements of engagement execution, including information gathering, process documentation, and coordination of deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance on change management, including communication approaches, training support, and adoption best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate timelines, milestones, and engagement activities to ensure work progresses effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal partners across product, delivery, and account teams to ensure alignment and consistency in recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
